ke":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:36:38.000Z","msg":"balun<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a54da989d3b623f082e5ba76060e03d1a3996c","tid":1479691,"uid":60967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80d39f6b85ea33d105e8f400728f548a22125c05","tid":1479691,"uid":32661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"816847a549251af60c0a79c34a5ad335090e48ab","tid":1479691,"uid":40826,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"447523285d0286ef83f958bdb18d481214ae5fde","tid":1479691,"uid":60967,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T04:26:59.000Z","msg":"因為整大左成本貴左<br />\n如果整大左仲要賣得平,應該賣一粒蝕一粒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T10:30:49.000Z","msg":"其實係越大越平"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:36:19.000Z","msg":"你同一塊wafer開得少左chip仲要良率低左點解會平左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T16:29:13.000Z","msg":"佢應該攪錯左wafer size 同die size"},{"pid":"fb005c0172d79417f518e1b1a8c7857516c13007","tid":1479691,"uid":20664,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:26:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>研究機構 IHS Markit 早前拆解了 6 部在市場發售中的 5G 手機，然後針對晶片體積、系統設計和記憶體進行分析，結果發現華為的 Balong 5000 5G Modem 不但體積最大，而且比起競爭對手更加昂貴，同時亦更加耗電。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBalong 5000 是首款同時支援 2G、3G、4G、5G 的 Modem 晶片，但由於 Mate 20X 5G 手機使用 Kirin 980 處理器已經內置了 2G、3G、4G Modem，兩者結合使用令 Kirin 980 的 Modem 變得沒用和多餘，浪費了電路板的空間之餘，亦增加了電池損耗和成本開支。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIHS Markit 又提到 Balong 5000 的體積較對手 Qualcomm Snapdragon X50 大了足足50%，支援的記憶體雖然達到 3GB，<span style=\"color: red;\">卻不能支援 mmWave 5G 網絡。</span>至於 Samsung 的 Exynos 5100 5G Modem，其體積亦跟 Snapdragon X50 幾乎一樣細，故IHS Markit 直指華為的設計最不理想。</blockquote><br />\n其實篇文好有問題<br />\nX50係純5G Modem，本身設計剩係用喺可擴充5G嘅SoC上面，即係855，所以一定會比X55同Balong 5000 2/3/4/5G多重模式modem細<br />\nBalong5000係支援mmWave同最重要嘅5G Standalone (aka 5G SA)，即係全native 5G網絡<br />\n呢樣嘢要X55先支援到，X50只係支援5G Non-standalone (aka 5G NSA)，即係有基於舊4G網絡技術規格嘅非原生5G<br />\nNSA同SA模式唔同，只支援5G NSA嘅機喺5G NSA完全過渡到5G SA之後未必可以再用到5G<br />\n有錯細力啲屌<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.qualcomm.com/products/snapdragon-x50-5g-modem\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qualcomm.com%2Fproducts%2Fsnapdragon-x50-5g-modem&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75RPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=45c2040f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.qualcomm.com/products/snapdragon-x50-5g-modem</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.qualcomm.com/products/snapdragon-x55-5g-modem\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qualcomm.com%2Fproducts%2Fsnapdragon-x55-5g-modem&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75RPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=ff683391\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.qualcomm.com/products/snapdragon-x55-5g-modem</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hisilicon.com/en/Products/ProductList/Balong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hisilicon.com%2Fen%2FProducts%2FProductList%2FBalong&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75RPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=3295fd0c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hisilicon.com/en/Products/ProductList/Balong</a>"},{"pid":"95aefb13b7072b6f4b12b5e084affd820aded990","tid":1479691,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:36:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>設計不理想可以理解，但係華為售價居然比對手貴？</blockquote>因為整大左成本貴左<br />\n如果整大左仲要賣得平,應該賣一粒蝕一粒</blockquote>相信<del><span style=\"color: red;\">芯</span></del>片製造成本只佔總體成本很小比例，大50%體制應該不會對成本造成很大影響</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n晶片呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}